overview: We take you on a journey around the world to check out never seen before footage of some of the top Breakdancers jamming and battling on the dance floor and the street. With practice sessions, shows, interviews, club sessions to crazy uncut battles, you see it all from first row. Featuring Europe Surf, Fuko,Delta Force and Floorock of Las Vegas.
title: Underground Breakdance: Part 2
